de.fhg.fit.biomos.sensorplatform.sensor

Interface SensorCommands

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractHeartRateSensor, AbstractPulseOximeterSensor, AdidasMiCoachHRM, BLE113, CC2650, PolarH7, Sensor, TomTomHRM

    public interface SensorCommands
    Defines methods, which are called from the corresponding SensorWrapper. Currently only two commands are supported, enable and disable notifications. Other commands can be added in the future (for example reading battery status).
    Author:
    Daniel Pyka

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      void disableAllNotification(BufferedWriter streamToSensor, String charWriteCmd, String disableNotification)
      Disable the measurement and notification of the sensor previously enabled.
      void enableAllNotification(BufferedWriter streamToSensor, String charWriteCmd, String enableNotification)
      Enable the measurement and notification of the sensor as defined in the settings of the sensor.
